They brought out the order and mine was right but my boyfriend's food was wrong and he had to wait another 15 to 20 minutes to get what he wanted.  Then we had to wait and finally flag down the waiter to get our check.  We got there between 8:30 and 9:00 PM and we got home about 10:15.  We live 5 minutes away.  It took us an hour and a half to order our food, get it, eat it, and get our check and pay for it.  It wasn't like we ordered a full meal, we had appetizers.
